    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>

          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Documents Related to Churchill and FDR</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dokumente in Verbindung gestanden auf Churchill 
und FDR</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Documents liés à Churchill et à FDR</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Originais relacionados a Churchill e a FDR</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Documenti relativi a Churchill ed al FDR</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Έγγραφα σχετικά με Churchill και FDR</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Documentos relacionados con Churchill y el FDR</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">examines the friendship and working relations that developed between U.S. President Franklin Roosevelt and British Prime Minister Winston Churchill beginning in 1940. Their relationship was crucial in the establishment of a unified effort to deal with the Axis powers.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">überprüft die Freundschaft und die 
Arbeitsrelationen, die zwischen VEREINIGTE STAATEN Präsidenten 
Franklin Roosevelt und britischer Premierminister Winston Churchill 
sich entwickelten, das 1940 anfängt. Ihr Verhältnis war in der
Einrichtung einer vereinheitlichten Bemühung, die Mittellinie 
Energien zu beschäftigen entscheidend.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">examine l'amitié et les relations fonctionnantes 
qui se sont développées entre le Président Franklin Roosevelt et 
premier ministre britannique Winston Churchill des ETATS-UNIS 
commençant en 1940. Leur rapport était crucial dans 
l'établissement d'un effort unifié de traiter les puissances d'axe.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">examina o friendship e as relações trabalhando 
que se tornaram entre o presidente Franklin Roosevelt e ministro 
principal britânico Winston Churchill de ESTADOS UNIDOS que começa 
em 1940. Seu relacionamento era crucial no estabelecimento de um
esforço unified tratar das potências da linha central.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">esamina l'amicizia ed i rapporti di funzionamento 
che si sono sviluppati fra il presidente Franklin Roosevelt ed il 
Primo Ministro britannico Winston Churchill degli STATI UNITI che 
comincia in 1940. Il loro rapporto era cruciale nell'istituzione
di uno sforzo unificato occuparsi delle potenzi di asse.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">εξετάζει τις σχέσεις φιλίας και εργασίας που 
ανέπτυξαν μεταξύ των ΗΠΑ τον Πρόεδρο Franklin Roosevelt και η
βρετανική αρχή Winston Churchill πρωθυπουργών σε 1940, η 
σχέση τους ήταν κρίσιμη στην καθιέρωση μιας ενοποιημένης 
προσπάθειας να εξεταστούν οι δυνάμεις άξονα.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">examina la amistad y las relaciones de trabajo que
se convirtieron entre presidente Franklin Roosevelt y primer ministro 
británico Winston Churchill de ESTADOS UNIDOS que comenzaba en 1940. 
Su lazo era crucial en el establecimiento de un esfuerzo 
unificado de ocuparse de las potencias del eje.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>

          <keyword>
